Pattern Recognition

📌 Hashing / Frequency Counting

Key Observation:

We don't care about the positions of characters.

We only care how many times each character appears.

Counting frequencies lets us verify availability in linear time.

------------------------------------------------------------

Interview Insight

Whenever a problem asks:

"Can I construct one string from another?"

or

"Are there enough occurrences of each element?"

think about using a frequency array or hash map instead of repeatedly searching through the string.
